@OrgID int, @RecruiterID uniqueiden..er, @Year int, @Month int
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT * FROM DBO.MonthlyObjec.ve mo INNER JOIN DBO.WeeklyObjec.ve wo ON mo.ID=wo.MonthlyObjec.veID WHERE Organiza.onId=@OrgID AND RecruiterID=@RecruiterID AND Year=@Year AND Month=@Month ORDER BY wo.StartDate
END
